<% if var(:score).nil? %>
  <%= var(:item) %> is new here. Doesn't have any karma yet- why not start it off?
<% elsif var(:score).to_i > 10 %>
  Hey, <%= var(:item) %> is doing pretty good with a karma of <%= var(:score) %> - bet you wish you were them :)
<% elsif var(:score).to_i > 0 %>
  Not bad, not bad, <%= var(:item) %> is just getting started. Got a karma of <%= var(:score) %>
<% else %>
  Wow, I didn't know karma could get so bad. <%= var(:item) %>'s got <%= var(:score) %>
<% end %>